    <item>
      <title>印度通胀率自 2019 年以来首次跌破印度储备银行目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/india-inflation-dips-below-rbi-target-for-first-time-since-2019</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度通胀率近五年来首次低于央行目标，但由于政策制定者希望看到价格持续下降，因此目前不太可能刺激降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/india-inflation-dips-below-rbi-target-for-first-time-since-2019</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 12:10:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大型科技股、医疗保健股和高收益股是逢低买入目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/big-tech-health-care-and-high-yield-stocks-are-dip-buying-targets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[八月份的开局令人眼花缭乱，美国股市受到经济动荡、企业盈利不佳以及全球日元套利交易解除的重创，这让华尔街开始寻找可能受到不公平惩罚的市场角落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/big-tech-health-care-and-high-yield-stocks-are-dip-buying-targets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 12:08:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚最大银行将增加贷款，因政府暗示将降低利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/biggest-kenyan-bank-to-boost-loans-as-state-signals-lower-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在肯尼亚政府释放降低利率的计划后，肯尼亚市值最大的银行 Equity Group Holdings Plc 计划在今年下半年将本土市场的贷款增加 5%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/biggest-kenyan-bank-to-boost-loans-as-state-signals-lower-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 12:07:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大皇家银行前首席财务官称，在因关系问题被银行解雇之前，她曾是首席执行官候选人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/royal-bank-rbc-ex-cfo-ahn-says-she-had-shot-at-ceo-post-before-bank-fired-her</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纳丁·安 (Nadine Ahn) 表示，她有机会成为第一位执掌加拿大皇家银行的女性，但后来因与同事的私人关系而被解雇。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/royal-bank-rbc-ex-cfo-ahn-says-she-had-shot-at-ceo-post-before-bank-fired-her</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 12:05:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>捷蓝航空启动 27.5 亿美元债券发售，以忠诚度计划为支撑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/jetblue-starts-2-75-billion-debt-sale-backed-by-loyalty-program</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷蓝航空公司已启动价值 27.5 亿美元的债券和贷款发售，该发售以其忠诚度计划为支撑，旨在筹集储备金并为一般公司用途提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/jetblue-starts-2-75-billion-debt-sale-backed-by-loyalty-program</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 12:02:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高温席卷欧洲，雅典郊区发生大规模山火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/half-of-greece-on-maximum-fire-alert-as-swaths-of-europe-bake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一场巨大的野火威胁着雅典郊区的村庄，迫使数千人撤离，房屋被烧毁，当地医院也面临危险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/half-of-greece-on-maximum-fire-alert-as-swaths-of-europe-bake</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 08:18:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯供应风险推动天然气价格上涨，欧洲能源价格飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/european-gas-trades-near-2024-high-luring-imports-of-lng</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对俄罗斯穿越乌克兰的管道供应存在担忧，欧洲能源价格飙升，天然气价格延续上周涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/european-gas-trades-near-2024-high-luring-imports-of-lng</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 08:07:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>捷克央行宣布谨慎降息 通胀加速</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/czech-inflation-quickens-as-central-bank-flags-cautious-easing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克 7 月份通胀意外加速，进一步表明央行在进一步放松货币政策方面需谨慎。克朗上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/czech-inflation-quickens-as-central-bank-flags-cautious-easing</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 07:09:32 GMT</pubDate>
